column1: # All should go through except bad_child
# Elvis id should be yago:Elvis, from the Wikipedia page
# Brand id should be yago:_brand, from the Wikidata ID (which will be something like wd:Q123, i.e., yago:Q123)
# Bad child id should be yago:_Bad_Child__bad_child, which is the label plus (as disambiguation) the Wikidata id
